y so you feel comfortable. The Magic Scroll trought spells system is just a joke for the mouse, DON'T use it, assign the spells and skills you use the most to your hotbar or you will get frustrated.- The new graphics are poorly optimized but have been getting MUCH better with the updates to the game. If you have played alot of the original the you will be dissapointed by how ugly some of the heroes look compared to what I remember from the original. Jack of blades face and your face when you are a little boy.- Menu and inventory layout it BAD, It takes way to long to get used to find things in the inventory. Which might make some people not use it and when you have you will miss some of the quests because you will need to use thing from your inventory to figure out how to solve the quest.So, Is this game worth 32€?Almost, It is just like the the original game but with better graphics and I would say that the gameplay is a bit outdated.But when it gets to sale for 20€ or less this game is worth your money. ^^"
